# UI & Frontend Aesthetics (Web App Development)

## 1. Design Philosophy
- **Rich Aesthetics**: Use vibrant colors, glassmorphism, and modern typography.
- **Visual Excellence**: Avoid default Bootstrap/Streamlit looks. Use custom CSS injection where possible.
- **Dynamic**: Implement hover effects and smooth transitions.

## 2. Technology Stack
- **Core**: Python (Streamlit) or Next.js (if requested).
- **Styling**: Vanilla CSS for flexibility. Avoid Tailwind unless requested.

## 3. Workflow
- Plan -> Foundation (CSS) -> Components -> Pages -> Polish.
- Always check for mobile responsiveness.
